      "title": "The King Needs Legal Air",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "b02-c04-p01",
          "type": "prose",
          "body_md": "When your king is in check, normal plans stop. You must get out of check by moving the king, blocking the line, or capturing the checking piece."
        },
